# DIAGRAMA DE CLASES SOBRE EL RESTAURANTE

```mermaid
classDiagram
direction UD

MenuItem <|-- Beverage
MenuItem <|-- MainCourse
MenuItem <|-- Dessert
Order "1" *-- "1..*" MenuItem

class  MenuItem{
    +str Name
    +int Price
    +calculate_total_price()  
    }
    
class Beverage{
    +int Volume_ml
    }

class MainCourse{
    +str Protein
    +str Side_dish
    }

class Dessert{
    +str Texture
    }

class Order{
    +list Item
    +add_item(item: MenuItem) 
    +calculate_total() int
    +apply_discount() float
    }

```
